<i>In the name of Allah, the merciful.</i>

00:06.122 --> 00:08.682
<i>All praises due to Allah,</i>
<i>Lord of all worlds.</i>

00:08.958 --> 00:10.858
<i>The one God to whom praise</i>
<i>is due forever.</i>

00:11.061 --> 00:13.825
<i>The one who came to us in the person</i>
<i>of Fard Muhammad...</i>

00:14.030 --> 00:17.557
<i>...and raised up the Honorable</i>
<i>Elijah Muhammad. Amen.</i>

00:20.303 --> 00:21.964
<i>How do you feel?</i>

00:22.305 --> 00:24.603
-<i>Who do we want to hear?</i>
-Malcolm X!

00:24.808 --> 00:26.901
<i>Are we gonna bring him on?</i>

00:27.143 --> 00:28.906
<i>Yes, we gonna bring him on.</i>

00:29.112 --> 00:31.842
<i>Let us hear from our minister,</i>
<i>Mr. Malcolm X!</i>

00:32.048 --> 00:35.279
<i>Let us bring him on with</i>
<i>a round of applause.</i>

00:42.425 --> 00:45.724
<i>I'm here to tell you that</i>
<i>I charge the white man.</i>

00:45.929 --> 00:49.660
<i>I charge the white man with being</i>
<i>the greatest murderer on earth.</i>

00:49.933 --> 00:54.097
<i>I charge the white man with being</i>
<i>the greatest kidnapper on earth.</i>

00:54.337 --> 00:57.602
<i>There's no place in this world that</i>
<i>that man can go...</i>

00:57.941 --> 01:01.274
<i>...and say he created peace</i>
<i>and harmony. Everywhere he's gone...</i>

01:01.611 --> 01:02.942
<i>...he's created havoc.</i>

01:03.179 --> 01:06.171
<i>Everywhere he's gone,</i>
<i>he's created destruction.</i>

01:06.449 --> 01:10.613
<i>So I charge him with being</i>
<i>the greatest kidnapper on this earth!</i>

01:10.854 --> 01:13.948
<i>I charge him with being the greatest</i>
<i>murderer on this earth!</i>

01:14.190 --> 01:18.456
<i>I charge him with being the greatest</i>
<i>robber and enslaver on this earth!</i>

01:18.695 --> 01:20.390
<i>I charge the white man...</i>

01:20.597 --> 01:25.034
<i>...with being the greatest swine-eater</i>
<i>and drunkard on this earth!</i>

01:25.301 --> 01:27.394
<i>He can't deny the charges.</i>

01:27.604 --> 01:31.700
<i>You can't deny the charges!</i>
<i>We're the living proof of those charges!</i>

01:31.975 --> 01:34.000
<i>You and I are the proof.</i>

01:34.944 --> 01:38.141
<i>You're not an American.</i>
<i>You are the victim of America!</i>

01:38.381 --> 01:41.214
<i>You didn't have a choice coming here.</i>
<i>He didn't say:</i>

01:41.484 --> 01:45.215
<i>"Black man, black woman, come over</i>
<i>and help me build America. "</i>

01:45.488 --> 01:47.718
<i>He said, "Nigger, get in the boat.</i>

01:47.991 --> 01:51.324
<i>I'm taking you over there to help me</i>
<i>build America. "</i>

01:52.495 --> 01:55.225
<i>Being born here</i>
<i>does not make you an American.</i>

01:55.498 --> 02:00.299
<i>You and I are not American. You're one</i>
<i>of the 22 million black people...</i>

02:01.104 --> 02:05.973
<i>...who are victims of America.</i>
<i>You and I, we've never seen democracy.</i>

02:06.242 --> 02:10.906
<i>There's no democracy in the fields</i>
<i>of Georgia. No democracy down there.</i>

02:11.748 --> 02:16.685
<i>We didn't see any democracy in Harlem,</i>
<i>Brooklyn, Detroit, Chicago.</i>

02:16.953 --> 02:20.218
<i>Ain't no democracy there.</i>
<i>We've never seen democracy.</i>

02:21.691 --> 02:23.750
<i>All we've seen is hypocrisy.</i>

02:25.261 --> 02:27.422
<i>We don't see any American dream.</i>

02:28.198 --> 02:31.258
<i>We've experienced only</i>
<i>the American nightmare.</i>

