05:10.159 --> 05:11.251
Don't be scared, son.

05:11.461 --> 05:14.157
You ain't got nothing to worry about.

05:14.364 --> 05:16.958
You in the hands of an expert.

05:17.166 --> 05:21.034
My hair was just like yours.
