05:37.053 --> 05:38.042
Hold tight.

05:38.454 --> 05:41.116
I thought you said
this would sting, Shorty.

05:42.058 --> 05:43.150
This ain't nothing.

05:43.359 --> 05:45.190
-Feel good, don't it?
-Real good?

05:45.395 --> 05:46.862
Yeah, it's all right.

05:47.063 --> 05:48.291
You'll feel better.

