It is heating up a bit.

05:51.267 --> 05:52.859
It's starting to heat up.

05:53.069 --> 05:54.001
It's okay.

05:54.203 --> 05:55.670
Feeling better, ain't it?

05:55.872 --> 05:58.466
-Just hold on.
-I'm holding, but it's heating.

05:58.674 --> 06:00.642
Gotta make it straight.

06:01.044 --> 06:03.069
That's what he told me too.

06:04.247 --> 06:06.807
I gotta get this out now.
It's starting--

06:08.251 --> 06:11.277
-Hold on.
-I'm holding, I'm holding.

06:13.890 --> 06:14.788
Give me a hand!

06:14.991 --> 06:16.253
Help me out! Hold him!

06:17.226 --> 06:18.921
We're going to the sink!

06:19.128 --> 06:20.891
I got to get up! I got to get up!

06:21.097 --> 06:22.564
-Cool it!
-Put water on it!

06:22.765 --> 06:23.732
More water!

06:23.933 --> 06:25.992
You're getting it in my eye!

06:26.669 --> 06:29.399
-How's it feel?
-Like there's no skin on my head!

06:29.605 --> 06:30.833
If you can talk, it's out.

06:31.040 --> 06:33.474
-How does it look?
-Can't tell yet.

06:33.676 --> 06:36.338
Is it straight?
I'm not doing it again.

06:36.779 --> 06:38.610
Let me dry it.

06:40.850 --> 06:43.011
