Reflecting all the rays
of the spectrum.

01:12:30.229 --> 01:12:31.355
The opposite of black.

01:12:36.635 --> 01:12:39.035
Free from spot or blemish.

01:12:41.106 --> 01:12:42.733
Innocent. Pure."

01:12:47.046 --> 01:12:49.606
Ain't this something?
"Without evil intent.

01:12:49.815 --> 01:12:50.975
Harmless.

01:12:51.450 --> 01:12:53.179
Honest, square-dealing...

