01:13:23.182 --> 01:13:26.174
Page one. The first word: "Aardvark."

01:13:30.122 --> 01:13:31.248
"Aardvark.

01:13:31.457 --> 01:13:34.358
Earth pig.
African, ant-eating mammal.

01:13:34.827 --> 01:13:36.226
Abacus:

01:13:36.428 --> 01:13:40.091
Chinese calculating instrument.

01:13:42.534 --> 01:13:43.660
Abaddon:

01:13:43.869 --> 01:13:47.327
