<i>that when you come out...</i>

01:22:01.666 --> 01:22:03.998
<i>...which won't be long,</i>
<i>come straight to us.</i>

01:22:04.202 --> 01:22:05.169
Next.

01:22:11.509 --> 01:22:12.999
What'll it be?

01:22:14.679 --> 01:22:16.078
