01:22:20.285 --> 01:22:22.344
<i>You write, thanking me.</i>

01:22:23.288 --> 01:22:27.520
<i>Don't thank me, thank Allah.</i>
<i>He did it all.</i>

01:22:30.228 --> 01:22:31.855
<i>Dear Brother Baines:</i>

