<i>Please thank Elijah Muhammad</i>
<i>for the money...</i>

01:22:35.934 --> 01:22:38.266
<i>...and tell him</i>
<i>I haven't written him...</i>

01:22:38.470 --> 01:22:40.438
<i>...because I've</i>
<i>not yet proven myself.</i>

01:22:40.639 --> 01:22:44.871
<i>But I have shared his teachings</i>
<i>with old running buddies in Harlem...</i>

01:22:45.076 --> 01:22:48.512
<i>...and with my main man, Shorty,</i>
