01:23:13.872 --> 01:23:17.933
<i>I greet you with the ancient words</i>
<i>of peace, "As-Salaam-Alaikum. "</i>

01:23:18.543 --> 01:23:21.774
<i>P.S. I finally copied out the</i>
<i>entire dictionary.</i>

01:23:23.381 --> 01:23:26.612
