01:23:28.186 --> 01:23:31.883
"The thief cometh not
but for to steal...

01:23:32.157 --> 01:23:35.820
...and to kill, and to destroy.

01:23:36.161 --> 01:23:37.822
But I am come...

01:23:38.396 --> 01:23:40.125
...that they might have life...

01:23:40.899 --> 01:23:44.391
