01:25:17.262 --> 01:25:21.221
I'm proving to you that Jesus was not,
to quote an Indian brother...

01:25:21.432 --> 01:25:23.923
...he was not a paleface.

01:25:25.970 --> 01:25:26.595
Amen.

01:25:27.405 --> 01:25:29.134
